data.title: Tinker Bell
authors: Contributors to Fabulous Character Kingdoms Wiki
data.meta_description: Tinker Bell is a tritagonist of Peter Pan. She is a Disney Fairy, who serves as a Peter Pan's sidekick. For full gallery of this character, see Tinker Bell/Gallery.
